headline: How Investors May Respond To NetApp (NTAP) Launching AFX Platform and Expanding Key AI Partnerships
summary: At its recent INSIGHT™ Customer Conference in Las Vegas, NetApp introduced the AFX storage system, new AI and cyber resilience capabilities, and announced expanded partnerships with Cisco, Red Hat, Google Cloud, Equinix, and OPSWAT, focusing on enabling enterprise AI adoption and hybrid cloud transformation.
